name: Baby's First Year Set
description: All of the skincare products you will need for baby's first year. Unscented, dye free,  all natural and specially formulated by Dr Hodge with your babies skin in mind.

name: All Natural Skin Creme
description: Here is a great skin creme in an 8 oz tub for you to slather on baby after baths.  We use Olive Oil instead of Mineral Oil and include no perfumes, or dye's.  Great for family members with eczema and sensitive skin.

name: All Natural Diaper Creme
description: Here is a great diaper creme in a giant tub for liberal use on your baby's bottom during the first year. We use a high concentration of Zinc Oxide as a barrier and a touch of olive oil rather than petroleum products.

name: Organic Scent Free Baby Body Bar
description: Here is a one in all solution for your infant's tender skin.  No Perfume, all organic, and a great safe way to bathe baby and have one hand free at all times.  Remember, infants only need a bath every other day or every third day!  A great body bar for the whole family and expecially for kids with eczema and sensitive skin.
